- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on proposing an improved protocol stack for V2V and V2I communications in HetVNETs. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper discusses autonomous driving technology and proposes new techniques to tackle potential challenges. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is possible as the paper may involve computer vision techniques for autonomous driving. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is possible as the paper may involve control systems for autonomous driving. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is possible as the paper may discuss security issues related to autonomous driving and V2V/V2I communications.
